message.content: cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI. The paper discusses the citation advantage of OA self-archiving, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper focuses on biomedical journals, which could be classified under cybernetics (cs.CY).
